(288, 43, NULL, 'textbook', 'arihant-ncert-exampler-problem-solutions-class-12-mathematics', 'ARIHANT NCERT EXAMPLER PROBLEM + SOLUTIONS CLASS 12 MATHEMATICS', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Problem-solving is just like other skills we need to master in life. To be good at it, we need to practice it</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">with the right approach. In view of this, DESM &amp;amp; NCERT has developed Exemplar Problems to provide a</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">large number of quality problems.</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Get your hands on the latest edition of “NCERT EXEMPLAR PROBLEMS-SOLUTIONS: MATHEMATICS”</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">which has been designed for class XII students to master the basic technique of problem-solving. This</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">book contains Explanatory &amp;amp; Accurate Solutions to all the questions given in the NCERT Exemplar</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">mathematics book. Besides this, two additional features, that is, Thinking Process and Note have been</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">included to enhance the learning and thinking abilities of students. Acquiring this book will be highly</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">useful to score best in school examinations and build foundation for entrance examinations. It offers:</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">1. An all-inclusive book of NCERT Exemplar Problem-Solution</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">2. Explanatory &amp;amp; accurate solutions to all questions</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">3. A thinking process to tell how to solve a problem</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">4. Notes are provided with special points</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">5. A great tool to learn each concept of mathematics in a complete manner</span>&nbsp;</p>\n', 1, 0, 543, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 337.50, 375.00, 0.00, '9789326197471', 49011010, '9789326197471', 0, '', '', '', '', 'ARIHANT NCERT EXAMPLER PROBLEM + SOLUTIONS CLASS 12 MATHEMATICS', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 289, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
