nd-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Divided into 4 sections giving full coverage to the syllabus</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Each chapter is supported by detailed theory, illustrations, and all types of questions</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Special focus on New Pattern Objective Questions</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Every chapter accompanies Chapter Practice for quick revision</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Supplemented with all types of questions</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Assertion- Reason and Case-Based Questions</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Sample Papers for thorough revision</span></li>\n</ul>\n', 1, 0, 543, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 355.50, 395.00, 0.00, '9789326196659', 49011010, '9789326196659', 0, '', '', '', '', 'ARIHANT ALL IN ONE CLASS 9 SOCIAL SCIENCE (H)', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 343, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
