ved examples</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Divided into 18 chapters giving full coverage to the syllabus</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Each chapter is supported by detailed theory, illustrations, all types of questions</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Every chapter accompanies Chapter Overview, NCERT Folder, Chapter Practice and Chapter Test for quick revision</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: avertaregular;\">Sample Papers for thorough revision</span>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n', 1, 0, 543, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 292.50, 325.00, 0.00, '9789326194594', 49011010, '9789326194594', 0, '', '', '', '', 'ARIHANT ALL IN ONE CLASS 8 SCIENCE ', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 353, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
