 Sans\", sans-serif;\">Detailed solutions given at the book end</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\"><strong>Free booklet containing chapterwise solved questions of JEE Main 2022 (all 22 sets) with this book</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Work Sans;\"><strong>Includes access to chapter-based tests as well as JEE Main 2022 papers as online tests on Cengage Digital App (Android/Windows/iOS)</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\n', 1, 0, 544, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 760.50, 900.00, 0.00, '9789355734921', 49011010, '113', 0, '', '', '', '', 'CENGAGE A TO Z PHYSICS FOR JEE MAIN & ADVANCED CLASS 11', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 387, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
(387, 43, NULL, 'textbook', 'cengage-inorganic-chemistry-for-jee-advanced-part-ii', 'CENGAGE INORGANIC CHEMISTRY FOR JEE (ADVANCED) PART - II', '<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Work Sans;\"><em>Inorganic Chemistry for JEE (Advanced): Part 2</em>, a Cengage Exam Crack Series® product, is designed to help aspiring engineers focus on the subject of inorganic chemistry from two standpoints:</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">To develop their caliber, aptitude, and attitude for the engineering field and profession.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">To strengthen their grasp and understanding of the concepts of the subjects of study and their applicability at the grassroots level.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Work Sans;\">Each book in this series approaches the subject in a very conceptual and coherent manner. While its illustrative, solved examples facilitate easy mastering of the concepts and their applications, an array of solved problems exposes the students to a variety of questions that they can expect in the examination. The coverage and features of this series of books make it highly useful for all those preparing for JEE Main and Advanced and aspiring to become engineers.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Updated as per the latest JEE Advanced syllabus</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">In the chapter “Qualitative Inorganic Chemistry”, topic “Test of Bicarbonates” has been added</span></li>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Includes questions and problems from previous years\' JEE Main and Advanced papers, which help aspirants understand the pattern of the questions asked in the examination</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Features the following types of problems:</span></li>\n</ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Single Correct Answer Type</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Multiple Correct Answers Type</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Linked Comprehension Type</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Matrix Match Type</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Numerical Value Type (including Integer Answer Type)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Archives – all sets of solved JEE Main 2021 Qs in Appendix and JEE Advanced 2021 Qs in chapters</span></li>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Provides detailed solutions/explanations to all types of exercises</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Supplemented with Revised and Updated Chapterwise/Topicwise Daily Practice Problems (DPP)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">On</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\"><strong>Cengage Digital</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">app:</span></li>\n</ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">3+ Hours of 10 Videos on Difficult Topics</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">380 MCQs as Chapterwise Assessments</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">95 Subjective Qs of JEE Advanced Level</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">2009–21 Chapterwise Solved JEE Main Qs</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(63,63,63);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Work Sans\", sans-serif;\">Solutions to JEE Main 2022 Qs will be added on the App after the exam</span>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n', 1, 0, 544, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 675.00, 849.00, 0.00, '9789355732408', 49011010, '112', 0, '', '', '', '', 'CENGAGE INORGANIC CHEMISTRY FOR JEE (ADVANCED) PART - II', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 388, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
