(407, 43, NULL, 'textbook', 'mtg-objective-ncert-at-your-fingertips-mathematics', 'MTG OBJECTIVE NCERT AT YOUR FINGERTIPS MATHEMATICS', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">“MTG Objective NCERT at your Fingertips is an unparallel book designed on the syllabus of 11th and 12th NCERT textbook. It gives chapter-wise NCERT notes for quick-and-easy revision of concepts, topic-wise MCQs aligned with NCERT content to check your progress. It has 100+ chapter-wise MCQs on an average to guarantee the complete revision of NCERT. It is the leading choice of Toppers’ and the pinnacle for JEE exams along with NCERT. Standing tall as amazon no. 1 best seller, this book is a must for JEE/BOARDS/CUET.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• Chapter-wise NCERT notes for quick yet thorough &amp; impactful revisions.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• Tabular texts &amp; Illustrative diagrams in HD pages for understanding.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• NCERT Based Topic-wise MCQs from each of NCERT to get firm grip on concepts.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• NCERT Exemplar Problem MCQs to develop a strong base &amp; go in-depth.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• Assertion Reason, Case Based Questions &amp; NV type questions &amp; HOTS to cover all question typologies.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• Exam Archive including Previous years’ &amp; other PMT exam’s questions.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• Practice Papers &amp; Model Test Papers to put final practice touch to your preparation.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• JEE Trend Indicator for understanding last 3 years’ analysis of JEE questions.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• For self-evaluation, progress checker has been added.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• Answer keys, hints and explanations are also added in the book for micro-level understanding.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">• Complementary access to Fingertips Achievers package worth Rs. 299/-“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p>\n', 1, 0, 547, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 675.00, 750.00, 0.00, '9789391191771', 49011010, '9789391191771', 0, '', '', '', '', 'MTG OBJECTIVE NCERT AT YOUR FINGERTIPS MATHEMATICS', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 408, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
