(411, 43, NULL, 'textbook', 'mtg-neet-champion-biology', 'MTG NEET CHAMPION BIOLOGY', '<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">MTG’s NEET Champion</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Biology</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">is an especially curated thoughtful guide for NEET aspirants to turn their dreams into reality. The book provides 10 previous years questions of the NEET exam along with solutions for an ultimate study experience. Approximately, 90% of the MCQs in the NEET exam are same or similar from the MTG NEET Books. The 100% solved NEET question bank provides 5000+ questions in a chapter-wise and topic-wise format from previous years’ medical entrance exams. MTG’s mission through this book is to help students know what to expect in the NEET exam and feel confident about how to attempt it. The objective is to familiarize students with the question typology frequently asked in the NEET exam. The process helps students gain mastery over the subjects. Hence, they emerge as the ultimate NEET Champions.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">5000+ questions from previous 10 years’ medical entrance exams in a chapter-wise and topic-wise format.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">Graphical analysis of questions highlighting weightage of topics.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">Book is divided into two parts chapter-wise according to the syllabus of class 11 and class 12.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">Concise and refreshing theory for effective and final revisions.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">NCERT based chapter-wise and topic-wise segregation of previous 10 years’ questions of NEET entrance exams. (2022-2013)</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">10 Unit tests consisting level-wise questions for self-evaluation and practice.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">5 Model test papers as per the latest pattern for NEET exam by NTA to check the progress and readiness of the preparation.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">100% error-free and 100% solved book with hints and explanations for better understanding and self-analysis check.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></li>\n</ul>\n', 1, 0, 547, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 810.00, 900.00, 0.00, '9789355551924', 49011010, '9789355551924', 0, '', '', '', '', 'MTG NEET CHAMPION BIOLOGY', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 412, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
