(414, 43, NULL, 'textbook', 'mtg-neet-guide-chapterwisw-topicwise-biology', 'MTG NEET GUIDE (CHAPTERWISW & TOPICWISE) BIOLOGY', '<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">The Complete NEET Guide Chapter-wise topic-wise Biology is the latest revised key by MTG to assist you in the initial learning phase of NEET 2023. MTG’s NEET Guide is the most successful title to cover the NEET syllabus. The book claims that around 90% same or similar questions are asked in the NEET-UG entrance exam. The book covers the syllabi of classes 11 &amp; 12 to accommodate the latest syllabus of the NEET exam. The comprehensive coverage of theory, illustrations, and chapter-wise concept maps help in a detailed understanding of the theory.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57,57,57);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial;\">The exam-café section incorporated in each chapter provides objective questions for practice along with answer keys and detailed solutions. To educate you about what type of questions are asked on each topic, the previous 10 years’ questions (2013-2022) are provided in a chapter-wise bifurcated manner. To keep you updated with the latest NEET exam trends, the latest NEET-UG 2022 paper is solved and incorporated into the book. This book is for CBSE and Non- CBSE students and gives an advantage of the thorough practice of AIPMT/NEET chapter-wise questions.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p>\n', 1, 0, 547, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0.00, 810.00, 900.00, 0.00, '9789355551689', 49011010, '9789355551689', 0, '', '', '', '', 'MTG NEET GUIDE (CHAPTERWISW & TOPICWISE) BIOLOGY', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 'erp_textbooks', 415, '2026-02-28 05:39:28', '2026-02-28 10:07:04', NULL, NULL),
