(417, 43, NULL, 'textbook', 'golden-guide-class-10-mathematics', 'GOLDEN GUIDE CLASS 10 MATHEMATICS', '<ul>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">As per New NCERT Textbooks</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">Based on the latest syllabus of CBSE</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">Summary &amp; Word Notes in English &amp; Hindi</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">Important Passages for Comprehension with Questions &amp; Answers</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">Solved NCERT Textual Exercises of Honeysuckle and A Pact with Sun</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">Additional Important Questions with Answers</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">Objective Type Question Bank (With Answers)</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">MCQs.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108,108,108);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: poppins;\">Paragraph Based Questions.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-left:1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34,34,34);background-color: rgb(255,2